sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant Job as LMEval Job Pod<br/>User 65532:65532
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3-Compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RemoteAPI as Remote LM API<br/>Configurable Port
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Operator,Job: Flow 1: Job Creation
    Operator->>Job: Create K8s Job<br/>(LMEvalJob CR triggers)

    Note over Job,HFHub: Flow 2: Local Model Evaluation
    Job->>HFHub: GET /models/{model_id}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (HF_TOKEN)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    HFHub-->>Job: Model weights, tokenizer, config
    Job->>Job: Load model locally (HF/vLLM)<br/>Run evaluation tasks<br/>Compute metrics (50+ offline)
    Job->>Job: Write results to /opt/app-root/src/output

    Note over Job,S3: Flow 3: S3 Model Download
    Job->>S3: GET (boto3 S3 API)<br/>Auth: AWS Signature V4<br/>TLS 1.2+ (AWS_CA_BUNDLE)<br/>Verify: S3_VERIFY_SSL
    S3-->>Job: Model artifacts
    Job->>Job: Cache model locally<br/>Run evaluation

    Note over Job,RemoteAPI: Flow 4: API-Based Evaluation
    Job->>RemoteAPI: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>Encryption: Configurable TLS<br/>verify_certificate flag
    RemoteAPI-->>Job: Completion response
    Job->>Job: Score responses against benchmarks

    Note over Job,OCI: Flow 5: OCI Result Publishing
    Job->>OCI: PUT (skopeo/OCI Distribution API)<br/>Auth: Docker config or username/password<br/>TLS 1.2+ (OCI_VERIFY_SSL)
    OCI-->>Job: Artifact push confirmation

    Note over Job: Job completes and pod terminates
